(24093, 220, 'text_curaprox', '<strong>CURAPROX Baby</strong> – the newest member of the CURAPROX family, the Swiss brand that’s all about oral health. And just like the rest of the CURAPROX range, the products by CURAPROX Baby are backed by leading experts. Curaprox is a brand of Curaden AG, which is headquartered in Kriens, Switzerland. Since 1972, Curaprox has been working with expert researchers, academics and practitioners to develop oral health devices that are as gentle and effective as possible. The luxury brand Swiss smile also belongs to Curaden AG. And now Curaden AG has developed a revolutionary new prevention program: Prevention One.'),
